ADMIN NOTE Hi everyone!
This is a worldwide group! And some shows/movies may not be streaming in your country unless they are “Netflix original”shows.
Due to licensing restrictions, a large number of Netflix shows are region specific. No need to say it is “not on Netflix”.
Also,to verify what country a show is streaming on Netflix we utilize unogs.com. Check it out
Try the Justwatch app to find what platform a show is streaming on in your country. Another resource is to search Facebook for our Netflix recommendations satellite group for your country🤩Cheers😁 and
Happy Netflixing!

Do not respond to said comments as this just creates more attention to their post. To report a comment, click on the comment and choose report to group admins. Try not to report the entire post as it is almost impossible to search for it, especially if it is a popular post in a group of 3.7million members. The admin team really appreciate your help Thanks 🍿🎥🎞🍿
